countries_page = BeautifulSoup(response.text, 'lxml') # beautiful soap

countries_data = table_countries.find_all('td')
countries = [i.text for i in countries_data]

countries = [countries[i].split(" ", 1) for i in range(len(countries))]
countries0 = []
countries1 = []
for i in range(len(countries)):
    countries0.append(countries[i][0])
    countries1.append(countries[i][1])
countries_dict = dict(zip(countries1, countries0))

import pandas as pd

def parse_airports(country):
    url_country = f'http://www.fallingrain.com/world/{countries_dict[country]}/airports.html'
    response = requests.get(url_country)
    page = BeautifulSoup(response.text, 'lxml')
    table1 = page.find('table')
    headers = []
    for i in table1.find_all('th'):
        title = i.text
        headers.append(title)
    country_data = pd.DataFrame(columns = headers)
    for j in table1.find_all('tr')[1:]:
        row_data = j.find_all('td')
        row = [i.text for i in row_data]
        length = len(country_data)
        country_data.loc[length] = row
    return country_data

In [3]:
import re

def airports_of_the_country(df):
    df = df.replace('', pd.NA)
    for i in range(len(df['Latitude'])):
        df.loc[i, 'Latitude'] = float(re.sub(r"...$", "", df.loc[i, 'Latitude'])) #   ,     
        df.loc[i, 'Longitude'] = float(re.sub(r"...$", "", df.loc[i, 'Longitude']))
    return df

Функция расстояния между двумя точками на земном шаре¶

networkx , ,

x1, y1 x2, y2 ,

In [4]:
import numpy as np

def distance(x1, y1, x2, y2):
    x1 = np.radians(x1)
    x2 = np.radians(x2)
    y1 = np.radians(y1)
    y2 = np.radians(y2)
    r = 6372.7
    delta_y = y2 - y1
    delta_x = x2 - x1
    a = ( np.sin(delta_x/2) )**2 + np.cos(x1)*np.cos(x2)*(np.sin(delta_y/2))**2
    dist = 2*r*np.arcsin(np.sqrt(a))
    return dist

Отображение графа аэропортов, между которыми расстояние меньше определенного¶

, , , , max_dist

In [39]:
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import networkx as nx
import pandasql as ps #  ,     

def possible_to_fly_graph(country, max_dist):
    df = airports_of_the_country(country)
    p = nx.Graph()
    for i in range(len(df)):
        for j in range(len(df)):
            dist = distance(df.loc[i, 'Longitude'], df.loc[i, 'Latitude'], df.loc[j, 'Longitude'], df.loc[j, 'Latitude'])
            if i != j and dist < max_dist:
                p.add_edge(df.loc[i, 'Name'], df.loc[j, 'Name'])
    nx.draw(p, with_labels = False, node_size = 10, pos=nx.circular_layout(p))  #  
    plt.show

def possible_to_fly_medium_large_graph(country, max_dist):
    df = airports_of_the_country(country)
    select_df =  """SELECT Name, Latitude, Longitude 
                    FROM df 
                    WHERE (Kind = 'Medium' or Kind = 'Large')"""
    df = ps.sqldf(select_df, locals()) #  sql
    
    p = nx.Graph()
    for i in range(len(df)):
        for j in range(len(df)):
            dist = distance(df.loc[i, 'Longitude'], df.loc[i, 'Latitude'], df.loc[j, 'Longitude'], df.loc[j, 'Latitude'])
            if i != j and dist < max_dist:
                p.add_edge(df.loc[i, 'Name'], df.loc[j, 'Name'])
    nx.draw(p, with_labels = False, node_size = 10, pos=nx.circular_layout(p))  #  
    plt.show

def airports_on_the_map(country):
    df = airports_of_the_country(parse_airports(country))
    gdf = gpd.GeoDataFrame(df, geometry=gpd.points_from_xy(df.Longitude, df.Latitude), crs="EPSG:4326")
    cnry_map = world_map.loc[world_map['ADMIN'] == country]
    ax = cnry_map.plot(color="white", edgecolor="black")

    gdf.plot(ax=ax, color="red",  markersize=1)

    plt.show()

def airports_on_the_map_medium_large(country):
    df = airports_of_the_country(parse_airports(country))
    select_df =  """SELECT Name, Latitude, Longitude 
                    FROM df 
                    WHERE (Kind = 'Medium' or Kind = 'Large')"""
    df = ps.sqldf(select_df, locals()) #  sql
    gdf = gpd.GeoDataFrame(df, geometry=gpd.points_from_xy(df.Longitude, df.Latitude), crs="EPSG:4326")
    cnry_map = world_map.loc[world_map['ADMIN'] == country]
    ax = cnry_map.plot(color="white", edgecolor="black")

    gdf.plot(ax=ax, color="blue",  markersize=1)

    plt.show()

Функция построения круговой диаграммы видов аэропортов¶

In [34]:
def airports_of_different_kinds(country):
    df = airports_of_the_country(country)
    select_df = """
        SELECT Kind, COUNT(*)
        FROM df
        GROUP BY Kind
    """
    df = ps.sqldf(select_df, locals())
    fig, ax = plt.subplots()
    ax.pie(df["COUNT(*)"], labels = df["Kind"])
    ax.axis("equal")
    plt.show()
